snippet.title: Jellies of the Deep - Trailer Wholesome Games | A Relaxed Hidden Object Game
snippet.description:
Coming to Steam this November. Wishlist now!
We are proud to be part of Wholesome Games Steam Celebration, from Aug 15 to 21, 2024. See you there!

Jellies of the Deep is a hidden object and spot-the-difference game in one. Visit secret spots below the ocean to find special, one-of-a-kind jellies hiding in plain sight. Features:
•⁠ Relaxed gameplay, no time limits
•⁠ 20 colourful hand-drawn levels
•⁠ 60 cute creatures to collect and name

STEAM STORE: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3020970/Jellies_of_the_Deep/?beta=0
WHOLESOME GAMES AT STEAM:  https://store.steampowered.com/sale/wholesomegames
WEBSITE:  https://jelliesofthedeep.com
